nodes.text: MSE-6 Series Repair Droid Souvenir Popcorn Vessel

The MSE-6 Series Repair Droid Souvenir Popcorn Vessel was a souvenir popped grain bucket made from an MSE-6 series repair droid and sold at Kat Saka's Kettle in Black Spire Outpost on the Outer Rim planet Batuu. It was used to hold the Outpost Mix.
